title: Good Omens - Rewrite the Stars - Crowley and Aziraphale
author: gabygogo505
comment: I don't know why this hasn't gotten more attention.  This is an excellent song for them!
This is truly Aziapheal and Crowley’s song!! Beautiful video! 😍💖
Oh this is absolutely brilliant! Bravo!
description:
Re-uploaded due to better inspiration (literally just added one clip that made it 200% better). I absolutely adore these two characters! I just finished Good Omens (for the second time) and still cannot get enough! David Tennant and Michael Sheen's chemistry as Crowley and Aziraphale is undeniable and no one could have done a better job! Congrats to the cast and crew for an ineffable mini-series. Fantastic! Thank you to Neil Gaiman and Terry Pratchett (RIP) for creating these characters! Per the usual, I do not own the song nor the rights to the show, just the editing.

Song: Rewrite the Stars by Pasek and Paul, performed by Zac Efron and Zendaya in "The Greatest Showman"
